{"id":"7cd927669522","content":"In this two-for-one episode recorded at HumanX, Ryan is first joined by Christine Yen, CEO of Honeycomb, to discuss how AI compresses the software development lifecycle, making observability about capturing the right telemetry. Then, Spiros Xanthos, founder and CEO of Resolve AI, shares with us how AI coding increases code volume but decreases human intuition, making production operations harder than ever. ​​​​‌﻿‍﻿​‍​‍‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‌﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿‍​‍​‍​﻿‍‍​‍​‍‌﻿​﻿‌‍​‌‌‍﻿‍‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌​‍﻿‍‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿﻿​‍​‍​‍﻿​​‍​‍‌‍‍​‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‌‌‍‌‍​‍​‍​﻿‍‍​‍​‍‌‍‍​‌﻿‌​‌﻿‌​‌﻿​​‌﻿​﻿​﻿‍‍​‍﻿﻿​‍﻿﻿‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿‌‌﻿​﻿​‍﻿‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‍﻿‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿﻿​‍﻿﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​‌‍‌‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​​‍﻿﻿‌‍‌‌‌‍‌​‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌​​‍﻿﻿‌‍﻿‌‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌﻿​​‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿﻿‌‍﻿‍​﻿‍﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​​﻿﻿‌​﻿‌‌​﻿​‌‌‍‌‌​﻿​‍​﻿‌‍​﻿‌​​﻿‌‍‌‍​‍​‍﻿‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‌​​﻿‌‍‌‍​‍​‍﻿‌​﻿‌​​﻿‍‌​﻿‌﻿​﻿​​​‍﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍‌‌​﻿‍​​﻿​‍​‍﻿‌​﻿‌‌‌‍‌‌‌‍​‍‌‍​‌‌‍‌‍‌‍​﻿​﻿​‌‌‍‌‍​﻿‌﻿​﻿‍​​﻿‌​​﻿​‌​﻿‍﻿‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌﻿‌‌​​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​​﻿‍﻿‌﻿​​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌﻿‍​‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​​‌﻿‌​​﻿﻿﻿‌‍​‍‌‍​‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌‌‌‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍﻿​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‍​‌﻿‌​‌﻿‌​‌﻿​​‌﻿​﻿​‍‌‌​﻿​﻿‌​​‌​‍‌‌​﻿​‍‌​‌‍​‍‌‌​﻿​‍‌​‌‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿‌‌﻿​﻿​‍﻿‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‍﻿‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​​﻿﻿‌​﻿‌‌​﻿​‌‌‍‌‌​﻿​‍​﻿‌‍​﻿‌​​﻿‌‍‌‍​‍​‍﻿‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‌​​﻿‌‍‌‍​‍​‍﻿‌​﻿‌​​﻿‍‌​﻿‌﻿​﻿​​​‍﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍‌‌​﻿‍​​﻿​‍​‍﻿‌​﻿‌‌‌‍‌‌‌‍​‍‌‍​‌‌‍‌‍‌‍​﻿​﻿​‌‌‍‌‍​﻿‌﻿​﻿‍​​﻿‌​​﻿​‌​‍‌‍‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌﻿‌‌​​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​​‍‌‍‌﻿​​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌﻿‍​‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​​‌﻿‌​​‍‌‍‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌‌‍​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌﻿​​‌﻿‌‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍‍‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‍​‌‍‌‌‌‍‌​​‍​‍‌﻿﻿‌"}